{"tid":936882,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"特區護照射唔住","createTime":"2018-12-11T06:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T01:41:15.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdc65807d5d062207a6a15e68de6e7531e719e7","tid":936882,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:14:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20181211/20565733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181211%2F20565733&d=WTx8YifNbAy2WvdCmHyJUE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=e9442a17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181211%2F20565733&h=ac9c272b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/陳也/daily/article/20181211/20565733</a><br />\n<br />\n特區護照射唔住 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20181211/large/e8813a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20181211%2Flarge%2Fe8813a.jpg&h=8e4835c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n繼肥平後，另一件最低門檻都會判監30年的跨國重案爆出。華為公主在加拿大轉機時被抓，環球時報老編竟然以iPhone發文，明撐實攞景，被網民酸爆。老總面皮厚過他的包皮，無懼酸民，繼續yes挨瘋，not me華為，身體上下半部都誠實。<br />\n<br />\n華為公主持特區護照被擒，她是永久香港居民，同時又是隱晦中國公民。特區護照射唔住，護「主」無功，跟強國生產的老翻避孕套無異，一射便穿！保安局可能跟環時老總一樣，用的是蘋果手機，唔知點處理華為的選項。保安局長中學訓導老師附身，即刻打電話問上頭攞指示。哦哦哦，知道知道，唔使幫拖，這個時機，唔適合出聲。人都周咗，等於樓都跳咗，去醫院都嘥車費！保安局向地區名校的管理層極速學懂了八字膊，華為公主，地位超凡，坐30年監又唔使死，除非開死因庭，香港保安局才要出席夾口供吧。慢慢舟與晚晚舟，中國確認，百分百是中國公民，護照到底擁有七定八本，都唔入香港數，OK？周，來得太晚，行埋肥平，一路好走。  <br />\n<br />\n陳也 <br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n地位顯赫 (尊子)"},{"pid":"ba4254e93b97f4f953a8f60dac1d1bb2a232a78e","tid":936882,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"香港真係比支那拖鳩死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5a62636870177d2a70780d6321e51ed2a4d597","tid":936882,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba4254e93b97f4f953a8f60dac1d1bb2a232a78e","tid":936882,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T06:28:15.000Z","msg":"香港真係比支那拖鳩死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T01:41:15.000Z","msg":"大家請記住：<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">連登乞衣樓豬&mdash;EDO脆餅#23833<br />\n<br />\n(被追擊後第&ldquo;6&rdquo;個新名<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：儲錢要供824（<span style=\"color: red;\">連我名都抄埋</span>））</span><br />\n<br />\n想買不死鳥風褸，點買先最抵？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/504716/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n乞衣仔經典語錄:<br />\n<br />\n&rdquo;<em><span style=\"color: blue;\">我：你食撚左飯未<br />\n你： 我食左屎啦 </span></em>&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乞衣仔你上水未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}